## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="d7029-106">此类提供用于标准 installUtil 安装.NET framework 中的接口。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d7029-106">This class provides an interface for the standard installUtil installer in the .NET framework.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d7029-107">包含自动化类的任何程序集应包括从此类型派生的类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d7029-107">Any assembly that contains Automation classes should include a class that is derived from this type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d7029-108">这将提供生成的自动化对象的架构、 将其安装到 WMI，并创建必需的提供程序注册代码的代码。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d7029-108">This will provide code that generates the schema of the automation objects, installs it into WMI, and creates the necessary provider registration code.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="d7029-109">下面的示例演示如何从派生类<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.DefaultManagementInstaller>类安装 WMI 提供程序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d7029-109">The following example shows how to derive a class from the <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.DefaultManagementInstaller> class to install a WMI provider.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// This is the installer class that installs an instrumented assembly.  
// To use the default project installer, simply derive a class from  
// DefaultManagementInstaller.  No methods need to be overridden.  
[System.ComponentModel.RunInstaller(true)]  
public class TheInstaller : DefaultManagementInstaller  
{ }  
```
